{ Blinking text #ps-blinking-text

  The code `5` causes text to blink, but does not work in all terminals or console such as for example → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/cmd_exe[`cmd.exe`]. It does, however, work
  in the → Windows/Terminal (`wt.exe`):
  gh|about-PowerShell|/host/ANSI/blink.ps1||

  The blink turn of code is `25`.

}
{ Bold and underlined text

  gh|about-PowerShell|/host/ANSI/bold-underlined.ps1||

  The codes to turn of bold and underline are `22` and `24`.

}

